title: All Purpose Shining Powder!
description: Pitambari Shining Powder is a gentle stain removal without scratching. It removes oil and other stains thereby giving shine & gloss to metal surfaces at home. Pitambari Shining Powder has added fragrance of sandalwood for pleasant application.

name: Boric Acid 200g- Hesh Herbal
title: A Great Pest-Control for your Home!
description: Boric acid has Anti-Septic, Anti-Fungal and Anti-Viral Properties. It has many different uses. Boric Acid is a great ingredient for pest control of all types. It keeps away ants, fleas, termites, silverfish and cockroaches. It fireproofs the furniture and helps in it’s preservation. It is used to treat yeast infection and also to adjust pH. Boric acid is also used as cleanser and stain-remover.

name: Preethi X ProDuo Mixer (1300W)
description:
Powerful 1300W Motor: Comes with a sealed oil-filled sintered bronze bushes and double ball bearing motor for commercial grinding.
Turbo Vent Technology : This technology ensures that the heat generated by the motor does not affect the ingredients inside the jar. Helps keep the mixer grinder body cool and increases the life of the motor.
Stainless Steel Jar & Blade : Xpro Duo mixer grinder houses 2 stainless steel jars. These jars are made using high quality stainless steel and high precision blades for best performance. They also go through water load test to ensure stability and endurance.
Sturdy Double Clamped Handles : It has sturdy ergonomically designed double clamped Handles which ensures easy and convenient grip. It also has high grade Nylon & Neoprene Couplers for smooth trouble – free operation.
Tripod Metal Motor Stand : Reduces vibration and enhances motor life.
Hassle Free Operation : 3 Point Lid Lock for hands free operation. Secure Jar Lock for vibration free operation.
